{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-puzzle-js","path":"/puzzles/medium/112","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2>Question</h2>\n<p>p and q are two points chosen at random between 0 &#x26; 1. What is the probability that the ratio p/q lies between 1 &#x26; 2?</p>\n<h2>Hint</h2>\n<p>Graph Shading. (Whenever we see two uniform random variables, we graph them up!)</p>\n<h2>Answer</h2>\n<p>0.25</p>\n<h2>Solution</h2>\n<p>Assume that the points are <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">x</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span></span></span></span></span> &#x26; <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">y</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span></span></span></span></span> respectively. We want to know if <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">/</mi><mi>y</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">x/y</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mord\">/</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span></span></span></span></span> is between 1 and 2.\nIf we plot this, the limits are <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">/</mi><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">x/y=1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mord\">/</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span></span> and <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">/</mi><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">x/y = 2</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mord\">/</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">2</span></span></span></span></span>.\nThus, the desired region is the area between lines <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">y=x</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span></span></span></span></span> &#x26; <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>x</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">/</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">y=x/2</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mord\">/2</span></span></span></span></span>.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 200px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"plot\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/65c403f64f72da60c3b30ee42389a238/56d15/112_plot.drawio.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/65c403f64f72da60c3b30ee42389a238/77dd4/112_plot.drawio.png 50w,\n/static/65c403f64f72da60c3b30ee42389a238/effb6/112_plot.drawio.png 100w,\n/static/65c403f64f72da60c3b30ee42389a238/56d15/112_plot.drawio.png 200w,\n/static/65c403f64f72da60c3b30ee42389a238/a8a0d/112_plot.drawio.png 300w,\n/static/65c403f64f72da60c3b30ee42389a238/d9f49/112_plot.drawio.png 400w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"eager\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>This region is <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>1</mn><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">/</mi><mn>4</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">1/4</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1/4</span></span></span></span></span> th of the rest.</p>","frontmatter":{"puzzleId":112,"difficulty":"medium","category":"probability","title":"Random Ratio"}}},"pageContext":{"puzzleId":112,"previousPuzzleRoute":"/puzzles/medium/111","nextPuzzleRoute":"/puzzles/medium/114","difficulty":"medium"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3649515864","764694655"],"slicesMap":{}}